OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be dry with
OL,6,Fsome sunny spells. This afternoon will
OL,7,Fremain dry with variable amounts of
OL,8,Fcloud and some sunny spells. Light
OL,9,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FClouding over this evening
OL,12,Fwith a few showers spreading from the
OL,13,Fnorth. Then cloudy for the rest of the
OL,14,Fday with some showery rain, turning
OL,15,Fdrier later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FAny showery rain soon clearing
OL,18,Faway to leave all parts with a dry day
OL,19,Falong with sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
